parameters:
\SE[14]Alright...! For now, I've made it this far! \SE[14]I
can vaguely see the shape starting to take form...!

\SE[89]Whoa! Don't suddenly start glowing like that...!!
\!\SE[15]You scared me!

\SE[16]You're making another shitty game, aren't you! I
definitely want to play it again! \SE[0]As your fan number
2, I can't miss out on a new release!

\SE[3]Hmm... I'm happy about it, but... \SE[4]This time, I
want to make something more serious, so it seems like it
will take more time.

\SE[7]Oh, is that so...? \.I wanted to play it, what a
shame.... \!\SE[8]But on the bright side, it means you're
working hard, right...?

\SE[16]Then, is there anything I can help with? \SE[0]You
always entertain me, after all. I want to contribute to your
creative power, even if it's just a little.

\SE[16]Hmm...! Borrowing someone's help...!? I see, so
that's also an option...! \SE[15]Let's see, what would be
good...
\SE[3] (Ah, it's a combination of shitty game.)

\SE[12] (It seems troublesome to get involved... \!\SE[19]
How about taking a walk in a scenic place today?)

\SE[16]Hey, let's make a shitty game together! \!\SE[0]I'm
sure you'll come to love it too!

\SE[16]Absolutely not!! I have absolutely no interest in
that! \SE[15]Even if I enter society, such skills will be of
no use!

\SE[4]There's no such thing as something that's useless in
this world. \SE[0]Any experience should definitely become a
part of a person's flesh and blood. Right, Vita? You can be
useful to society, right?

\SE[17]Will it be useful to society...!? \!\SE[14]I wonder
if debugging will be useful...? \.If we narrow it down to
the industry, well, maybe it will work...?

\SE[15] Mama also loves Vita's shitty game! Let's go
together to deliver it once it's finished! \SE[15] I'm sure
she'll be very happy!

\SE[15]Yes, it's decided! \SE[15]Now... let's go to the
endless work hell!

\SE[16]Alright, we can go anytime! \!\SE[0]Please give us
instructions!
\SE[12] (Somehow, I ended up getting involved in helping...)

\SE[10]People are working for the sake of my shitty game...!
\!\SE[35]Ugh...! I can't believe something so wonderful is
happening...!!

\SE[13]Alright, let's get started then! \!\SE[12]Seeing is
believing! \.First, take a look at the prototype version!

\SE[4]It's dangerous to move too much, you know? \SE[3]The
power of machines is amazing, so even an arm can be easily
severed.

I have my own room too... but I might prefer... spending
time here with everyone...

...As for Vega, you know... she drinks a lot of water while
studying, so she goes to the bathroom... quite frequently...

When I look at the flames, my heart becomes calm... The
flames here are the most comforting.
